        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Only need 128GB for that one weekend project? Rent it for two days instead of mortgaging your house. Return it when you realize you could've done it with 16GB.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">No Download Time</h3>
